description:
This course is designed to help you live more holistically. It is for anyone seeking to improve their mental and emotional well-being and ultimately, their life.

The course contents include guided meditations, exercises, techniques and downloadable resources all designed to help you gain a greater awareness of the underlying emotions, beliefs and programs that are holding you back from your greatest life.

Upon completion of this course you will have the requisite tools and awareness to live your life with greater happiness, success and freedom.
title: Overcome Barriers to Creating Your Greatest Life
